#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.standard\\_cauchy"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a standard Cauchy distribution with mode = 0."
msgstr "从模式为 0 的标准柯西分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:3 of
msgid "Also known as the Lorentz distribution."
msgstr "也称为洛伦兹分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:5 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。默认为 None，此时返回一个单一值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:9 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的分块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:11 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:13 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:16 of
msgid "**samples** -- The drawn samples."
msgstr "**samples** -- 抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:20 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:21 of
msgid "The probability density function for the full Cauchy distribution is"
msgstr "完整柯西分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:23 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"P(x; x_0, \\gamma) = \\frac{1}{\\pi \\gamma \\bigl[ 1+\n"
"(\\frac{x-x_0}{\\gamma})^2 \\bigr] }\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:26 of
msgid ""
"and the Standard Cauchy distribution just sets :math:`x_0=0` and "
":math:`\\gamma=1`"
msgstr "而标准柯西分布只是设定了 :math:`x_0=0` 和 :math:`\\gamma=1`"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:29 of
msgid ""
"The Cauchy distribution arises in the solution to the driven harmonic "
"oscillator problem, and also describes spectral line broadening. It also "
"describes the distribution of values at which a line tilted at a random "
"angle will cut the x axis."
msgstr ""
"柯西分布在受驱谐振子问题的解中出现，并且也描述了谱线的展宽。它还描述了"
"一条以随机角度倾斜的直线与 x 轴相交位置的分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_cauchy.standard_cauchy:34 of
msgid ""
"When studying hypothesis tests that assume normality, seeing how the "
"tests perform on data from a Cauchy distribution is a good indicator of "
"their sensitivity to a heavy-tailed distribution, since the Cauchy looks "
"very much like a Gaussian distribution, but with heavier tails."
msgstr ""
"在研究假设正态性的假设检验时，观察这些检验在来自柯西分布的数据上的表现，"
"是衡量它们对重尾分布敏感性的一个良好指标，因为柯西分布看起来非常像"
"高斯分布，但尾部更重。"

